Package: ETLDelphi
Title: Delphi/Delfi to OMOP CDM v5.4 ETL for DuckDB
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Adam", "Black", , "black@ohdsi.org", role = c("aut", "cre"), comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-5576-8701"))
  )
Maintainer: Adam Black <black@ohdsi.org>
Description: End-to-end ETL that transforms Delphi-2M synthetic patient
    health trajectories into OMOP Common Data Model v5.4 tables in DuckDB.
    Delphi-2M data is generated by a modified GPT-2 model trained on UK Biobank
    records (Shmatko et al., Nature 2025, doi:10.1038/s41586-025-09529-3).
    Uses a 3-layer pattern (src -> stg -> cdm) with deterministic integer IDs
    and configurable concept mapping.
URL: https://github.com/gerstung-lab/Delphi
